definitions.definition: A Near Eastern and Caucasian musical instrument related to the zither , dulcimer , or harp having either 26 strings and a single bridge , or 42 strings and two bridges.

main_definition: ( music ) A Near Eastern and Caucasian musical instrument related to the zither , dulcimer , or harp having either 26 strings and a single bridge , or 42 strings and two bridges.
